WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
As leaders, we all have more capability
for growth than we realize.

00:04.000 --> 00:08.500
I guarantee you, you will not find
a straight line to success.

00:08.500 --> 00:12.500
What you need is to continuously
learn something.

00:12.500 --> 00:14.500
So how do you do that?

00:14.500 --> 00:17.000
Role models around you.

00:17.000 --> 00:21.000
Mentors around you
who are fantastic leaders.

00:21.000 --> 00:26.500
And I will tell you — the best mentors
tell you things that you don't wanna hear.

00:26.500 --> 00:30.000
That's where the high performance happens.
